docs/source/functional-spec.md:799:| M02-FR-006 | System shall store active-member relaxation evidence for new / recent members. |
docs/source/functional-spec.md:935:| M05-FR-001 | System shall route appraisal package to Sanction Committee after Credit Manager submission. |
docs/source/functional-spec.md:936:| M05-FR-002 | System shall display eligibility, loan amount, purpose, compliance checks, borrowing history, risk and documentation completeness. |
docs/source/functional-spec.md:937:| M05-FR-003 | System shall apply approval matrix based on loan amount and exception status. |
docs/source/functional-spec.md:938:| M05-FR-004 | System shall require CFO + one Director approval for loans up to ₹5,00,000. |
docs/source/functional-spec.md:939:| M05-FR-005 | System shall require CFO + two Directors for loans above ₹5,00,000. |
